sults offer fundamental insights and theoretical guidelines on design of\nlarge-scale wireless networks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 12 May 2013 19:17:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 May 2013 17:52:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 16 May 2013 20:37:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-20"}
