ons\nat the LHC, and find that the reach at the LHC can be as large as $m_{\\hat\nq}\\simeq 800$ GeV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 12 May 2013 22:31:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-11-20"}
